      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (e.g., E_rel) with uncertainty bounds on both simulation and experiment required at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "Relative error was computed for hemolysis index at 4 of 5 operating points; experimental uncertainty bands were not propagated into the comparison metric as required by project requirements. Achieved level 3."
